Steps for preparing and running RVIC:

#========================================================#
# Run parameter part
# (This part only need to be run once if setup is not changed)
#========================================================#
Step 1. Prepare parameter run input files
   ## If converting from Lohmann routing: 
   #    run: './process/RVIC/convert_params_Lohmann2RVIC.scr'
   #        (need to prepare a config file)

Step 2. Prepare RVIC parameter run config file

Step 3. Run RVIC parameter:
    $source activate rvic
    $rvic parameters $rvic_parameter.cfg

#========================================================#
# Run convolution part
#========================================================#
Step 4. Prepare RVIC convolution run config file
    (VIC output should be converted to netCDF format; see README_run_vic_steps)

Step 5. Run RVIC convolution:
    $source activate rvic
    $rvic parameters $rvic_convolution.cfg
 



